        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Financing Lead Out of Water Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill allows the issuance of tax-exempt private activity bonds to finance the replacement of any privately-owned portion of a lead service line in a public water system. Specifically, the bill provides that the use of proceeds from such bonds for replacement of a lead service line does not constitute private business use.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
